question: List all customers that lives in France
Find product records that belong to the 'Trains' product line
Get payment records made by customer number 124
Show the customer name and order date for customers in 'France' who placed orders after '2005-01-01'
gold_sql: SELECT c.customerName, o.orderDate FROM customers c JOIN orders o ON c.customerNumber = o.customerNumber WHERE c.country = 'France' AND o.orderDate > '2005-01-01';
llm_generated_sql:
SELECT c.customerName, o.orderDate 
FROM orders o 
JOIN customers c ON o.customerNumber = c.customerNumber 
WHERE c.country = 'France' AND o.orderDate > '2005-01-01';

question: Count the total number of orders placed by each customer. Show the customer name and the order count
gold_sql: SELECT c.customerName, COUNT(o.orderNumber) AS order_count FROM customers c JOIN orders o ON c.customerNumber = o.customerNumber GROUP BY c.customerName;
llm_generated_sql: SELECT c.customerName, COUNT(o.orderNumber) FROM customers AS c JOIN orders AS o ON c.customerNumber = o.customerNumber GROUP BY c.customerNumber
